item.title: CVE-2023-7082|2024-08-02T08:50:07.933Z -- unknown -- import%20any%20xml%20or%20csv%20file%20to%20wordpress
item.description: The Import any XML or CSV File to WordPress plugin before 3.7.3 accepts all zip files and automatically extracts the zip file into a publicly accessible directory without sufficiently validating the extracted file type. This may allows high privilege users such as administrator to upload an executable file type leading to remote code execution.
